OL,3,CTwo men sentenced for killing 'loving'
OL,4,Cfather-of-two in Birmingham
OL,6,FTwo men have been jailed after a
OL,7,F"loving" father-of-two was killed in
OL,8,FBirmingham.
OL,10,FAli Salih Abdalaah, aged 36, was
OL,11,Fbeaten to death in a hallway in Brecon
OL,12,FTower, Guild Close in Ladywood, in
OL,13,FOctober 2022.
OL,15,FAfter a three-week trial earlier this
OL,16,Fyear, Dale Berry-Parkes, 32, from
OL,17,FBirmingham, was found guilty of
OL,18,Fmanslaughter.
