OL,3,CTwo men sentenced for killing 'loving'
OL,4,Cfather-of-two in Birmingham
OL,6,FHe has now been jailed for 10 years
OL,7,Ffor killing Ali and also the theft of
OL,8,Fa motor vehicle.
OL,10,FA second man, Hardi Hamad, aged 35,
OL,11,Falso from Birmingham, pleaded guilty
OL,12,Fto manslaughter with diminished
OL,13,Fresponsibility during the trial.
OL,15,FHe was sentenced to 11 years
OL,16,Fimprisonment, along with an extended
OL,17,Flicence period of five years, for
OL,18,Fmanslaughter and motor vehicle theft
OL,19,Fon Thursday (4 July).
OL,21,FWhat happened?
