OL,4,Cfather-of-two in Birmingham
OL,6,FAt around 6.20am on 8 October, Ali
OL,7,Fvisited a shop on Soho Road before
OL,8,Fmeeting a woman who he took back to
OL,9,Fhis flat shortly after.
OL,11,FPolice said a few hours later, the
OL,12,Fwoman called Hamad and Berry-Parkes
OL,13,Fclaiming she had been sexually
OL,14,Fassaulted.
OL,16,FThe two men then turned up outside
OL,17,FAli's front door and fatally attacked
OL,18,Fhim on his doorstep.
