OL,6,FWalking out the flat block, CCTV
OL,7,Ffootage showed Berry-Parkes throwing a
OL,8,Fset of car keys to Hamad which
OL,9,Fbelonged to Ali's red Kia.
OL,11,FHamad and Berry-Parkes then drove off
OL,12,Fin convoy in Ali's stolen vehicle and
OL,13,Fa Peugeot, the vehicle the men arrived
OL,14,Fin.
OL,16,FSeveral days later, both cars were
OL,17,Frecovered with false plates.
OL,19,FOn 12 October, Hamad and Berry-Parkes
OL,20,Fwere arrested after handing themselves
OL,21,Fin to a police station.
