OL,6,F'Loving father'
OL,8,FIn tribute to Ali, his family said:
OL,9,F"Ali was a very hard working, happy
OL,10,Fand kind man.
OL,12,F"He was a loving father who dedicated
OL,13,Fhis life to his children. He loved to
OL,14,Fwork within the community,
OL,15,Fvolunteering to help those less
OL,16,Ffortunate than himself.
