OL,6,F"Our lives have been shattered. As a
OL,7,Ffamily and community particularly his
OL,8,Fyoung children, we are all devastated
OL,9,Fby his death which has changed our
OL,10,Fchildren's lives forever."
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Laura
OL,13,FHarrison, from our Homicide Unit,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Two children have been left
OL,15,Fwithout a father due to the appalling
OL,16,Factions of Hamad and Berry-Parkes.
OL,18,F"My thoughts remain with Ali's family
OL,19,Fas they continue to come to terms with
OL,20,Fhis loss."
